1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
AegisOps Autopilot is a Track 4 production incident response agent.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
It turns ambiguous alerts into a traced remediation workflow.

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:15,000
The workflow starts with incident context and persistent operational memory.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Qwen Cloud diagnosis is supported by log, metric, change graph, and policy tools.

5
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:27,000
The agent council reviews evidence before proposing a narrow reversible plan.

6
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:33,000
Human approval gates block risky production mutation until an operator approves.

7
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:39,000
Tool evidence remains visible for audit even when remediation is paused.

8
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:44,000
The same tool surface is exposed through OpenAPI and MCP stdio.

9
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:49,000
Deterministic evals and ablations verify the full workflow against a baseline.

10
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Alibaba deployment proof and verification scripts are included for Devpost judges.
